{"tid":760652,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不知道從什麼時候開始，在什麼東西上面都有個日期","createTime":"2018-07-29T17:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T15:24:03.000Z","uid":84102,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3ec81874bf504e5b16d707366f155347c76aa336","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/010259_295e01626bbee023871134bd6902c665.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F010259_295e01626bbee023871134bd6902c665.png&h=c7f456d8&s={SIZE}\" />秋刀魚會過期，肉罐頭會過期，連保鮮紙都會過期，我開始懷疑，在這個世界上，還有什麼東西是不會過期的？"},{"pid":"ec4db3631b871cf452bacda7dce2a078a3c933f2","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"人最大的煩惱，就是記性太好。如果什麼都可以忘掉﹐以後的每一天將會是一個新的開始<img src=\"https://img.hypesphere.com/2014/07/gekc086g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.hypesphere.com%2F2014%2F07%2Fgekc086g.jpg&h=1c2aeaf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89c984c0232c4526a55c8155a9fc92f54bd004c2","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/010557_200eb3f6a7794dfb37144678fdd74a82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F010557_200eb3f6a7794dfb37144678fdd74a82.png&h=75c3fc7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「不如我地 由頭黎過。」"},{"pid":"111ffaeb1242942a9a4b2857c2730b8726dcb533","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/010824_8469d623c683144c2b326c50ca082f0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F010824_8469d623c683144c2b326c50ca082f0d.png&h=f4b6d8ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「如果多一張船票，你願不願意跟我一起走？」"},{"pid":"16196b6c2c596a47ac792020abab2fa12bee2d47","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/011014_9e3ba35295a64fabe4ddbb09f42b629b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F011014_9e3ba35295a64fabe4ddbb09f42b629b.png&h=b2987803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我跟何寶榮不一樣，原來寂寞的時候，所有的人 都一樣。"},{"pid":"f5a6b8ff6f4e50756a6cea56533d63bccb611e68","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"16196b6c2c596a47ac792020abab2fa12bee2d47","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/011014_9e3ba35295a64fabe4ddbb09f42b629b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F011014_9e3ba35295a64fabe4ddbb09f42b629b.png&h=b2987803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我跟何寶榮不一樣，原來寂寞的時候，所有的人 都一樣。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:11:09.000Z","msg":"一直以嚟我以為我跟何寶榮不一樣，原來寂寞的時候，所有的人 都一樣。"},{"pid":"a28890434f03c90b8f95663c4c7bf5e6c1fd91ce","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:14:25.000Z","msg":"為什麼要遷就我呢？遷就得一時，遷就不了一輩子，你和我在一起是不會快樂的。"},{"pid":"af218b1f352c64d050b7a0c964ae20ada72e922c","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:16:06.000Z","msg":"那天下午我做了個夢，我到了他的家，走出那房子的時候，我以為我會醒來，誰知道，原來有些夢是永遠不會醒的。"},{"pid":"4700dabe7ad01854342be0f76be0ea827dc76c4e","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"很多事情我都沒有告訴何寶榮，我並不希望他趕快好起來，他受傷的那段日子，是我們最快樂的時光。"},{"pid":"16a8f399acfcb629211fe42ed66152c44329bae2","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"我答應過阿輝把他不開心留在這裡。我不知道他那天晚上講過什麼，可能是錄音機壞了，什麼聲音都沒有，只有兩聲很奇怪的聲音，好像一個人在哭。"},{"pid":"3e62a516ac771f67b638cf7d4eea6e79e77ba8a7","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"一個人唔開心可以扮 但把聲就扮唔到"},{"pid":"e89c572a9cf65cccac33ea0c02f2024516070cd2","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:27:27.000Z","msg":"人有煩惱係因為記性太好。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「得唔到嘅永遠都係最好。」"},{"pid":"7c5ab2a9b90dc8082a4f01f1814ad66f01e94608","tid":760652,"uid":157669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"好地地廚師沙律 換咩炸魚薯條"},{"pid":"9987600585fd967b9fe654d97ed7f03a66e9e9ed","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:29:06.000Z","msg":"「我已經好耐冇坐過電單車，亦都好耐未試過咁接近一個人。我知呢條路唔係好遠，好快我會落車，不過呢一分鐘我覺得好暖。」<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/132834_aeb7d2d910c6fe8184d2cbb0472d9f65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F132834_aeb7d2d910c6fe8184d2cbb0472d9f65.png&h=36bae5a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ad49c44865f2adc3140295486e63c499ea61e5a","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c5ab2a9b90dc8082a4f01f1814ad66f01e94608","tid":760652,"uid":157669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"好地地廚師沙律 換咩炸魚薯條"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:30:22.000Z","msg":"宵夜都噉多選擇 何況係男朋友？"},{"pid":"f49ef8ade4c0391e3b6905015cab720939767822","tid":760652,"uid":121981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e89c572a9cf65cccac33ea0c02f2024516070cd2","tid":760652,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:27:27.000Z","msg":"人有煩惱係因為記性太好。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「得唔到嘅永遠都係最好。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"連想得既機會都唔俾我 就俾咗第二個"},{"pid":"6e2b584e7e44623b3